<TEXT>
a legal struggle to decide who is 
the wife of the slain heroecologist francisco chico mendes 
could thwart efforts of international filmmakers to make a movie of 
his life 
eunice feitosa de menezes who claims to be mendes first and 
only legal wife has asked a court in acre his home state to 
confirm her marital status so she can contest any film rights 
allotted the recognized widow ilzamar mendes 
mendes 44 a rubber tappers union leader who fought to save the 
amazon from deforestation was killed by the son of a cattle 
rancher dec 22 outside his modest wooden house in xapuri 2666 
miles northwest of rio de janeiro 
mendes had won a united nations award for his struggle against 
amazon ranchers wanting to clear the rain forests for grazing 
hollywood producers seeing dramatic value in a story about a 
confrontation between powerful amazon landowners and humble rubber 
tree tappers have been turning up in brazil to see about shooting 
a movie about mendes regarded by many as the worlds first 
environmental martyr 
gilson pescador a member of the chico mendes foundation said 
offers have come from robert redford representing 20th century 
fox from united artists paramount pictures warner bros inc 
ted turner from atlanta and a number of british and brazilian film 
companies 
for the moment the decision on who will get the authorized film 
